#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/funqy-aws-lambda-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Funqy HTTP Binding with AWS Lambda "
msgstr "Funqy 与 AWS Lambda 的 HTTP 绑定"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/funqy-aws-lambda-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "<a class=\"status-label status-preview\" title=\"This extension's backward compatibility and presence in the ecosystem is not guaranteed\" href=\"#extension-status-note\">preview</a>"
msgstr "<a class=\"status-label status-preview\" title=\"无法保证此扩展程序的向后兼容性及其在生态系统中的可用性\" href=\"#extension-status-note\">预览</a>"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/funqy-aws-lambda-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you want to allow HTTP clients to invoke on your Funqy functions on AWS Lambda, Quarkus allows you to expose multiple\n"
"Funqy functions through HTTP deployed as one AWS Lambda.  This approach does add overhead over the\n"
"regular Funqy AWS Lambda integration and also requires you to use AWS API Gateway."
msgstr "如果您希望允许 HTTP 客户端调用您在 AWS Lambda 上部署的 Funqy 函数，Quarkus 支持您通过 HTTP 方式将多个 Funqy 函数作为单个 AWS Lambda 函数进行部署。这种方法相较于常规的 Funqy AWS Lambda 集成确实会增加一些开销，并且还需要您使用 AWS API Gateway。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/funqy-aws-lambda-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Follow the xref:aws-lambda-http.adoc[AWS Lambda Http Guide].  It walks through using a variety of HTTP\n"
"frameworks on AWS Lambda, including Funqy."
msgstr "请参考《 xref:aws-lambda-http.adoc[AWS Lambda HTTP 指南] 》。该指南详细介绍了如何在 AWS Lambda 上使用各种 HTTP 框架，包括 Funqy。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/funqy-aws-lambda-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The Funqy HTTP + AWS Lambda binding is not a replacement for REST over HTTP.  Because Funqy\n"
"needs to be portable across a lot of different protocols and function providers its HTTP binding\n"
"is very minimalistic and you will lose REST features like linking and the ability to leverage\n"
"HTTP features like cache-control and conditional GETs.  You may want to consider using Quarkus's\n"
"Jakarta REST, Spring MVC, or Vert.x Web Reactive Route xref:aws-lambda-http.adoc[support] instead.  They also work with Quarkus and AWS Lambda."
msgstr "Funqy 的 HTTP + AWS Lambda 绑定并不能替代基于 HTTP 的 REST。由于 Funqy 需要在多种不同协议和函数提供商之间保持可移植性，因此其 HTTP 绑定设计非常精简，您将无法使用 REST 的某些功能（如链接），也无法利用 HTTP 的某些特性（如缓存控制和条件 GET 请求）。 您不妨考虑改用 Quarkus 的 Jakarta REST、Spring MVC 或 Vert.x Web Reactive Route xref:aws-lambda-http.adoc[支持] 。这些方案同样兼容 Quarkus 和 AWS Lambda。"

